column5: Hoping Santa was good to you all !!  Leah really loves her new Troll Master Pro 2 !  She can't wait for me to get it installed on the kicker motor (and I'll give a full report on the install when it happens), so she doesn't have to play with the throttle anymore... while the rigger loader is yelling at her!
Leah got a great present there  I am sure you she will enjoy it
You spoil her way too much Wayne.
A merrry Christmas to you and yours.
I wonder if she has any idea just how lucky she is? Best wishes for Christmas and the new year!!! Jim
Hmmm. I would say that was a self-serving gift.... She's a lucky gal, after all she's not married to me
Merry Christmas and the best of health to all,  and here's hoping the travllers don't get smacked too hard by the lousy weather showing on the radar map.
Merry Christmas Wayne. All the best to you and your family!
